N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 10 ยง 451.160 - Inpatient bed occupancy ratio

State Regulations

The proportion of inpatient beds occupied, defined as the
ratio of inpatient service days to inpatient bed count days in the period under
consideration. Notes
